    "updated_at": "2024-06-26T14:51:28Z",
    "body": "If anyone wants to reproduce this, you can create a minimal ubuntu 22.04 docker container with starship prompt:\r\n```sh\r\ndocker run -it ubuntu:22.04 /bin/bash -c \"apt-get update && apt-get install -y curl && curl -sS https://starship.rs/install.sh | sh -s -- --yes && echo 'eval \\\"\\$(starship init bash)\\\"' >> ~/.bashrc && /bin/bash\"\r\n```\r\nHere's a video showing the wrapping issue:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/starship/starship/assets/20020722/fb260686-5aa1-45eb-ab40-fb70f6fe89cf\r\n\r\n",
