    "body": "For docker, the minimum required seems to be:\r\n\r\n```dockerfile\r\nRUN export DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive && apt-get update && apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends locales\r\n\r\nRUN locale-gen \"en_US.UTF-8\"\r\n\r\nENV LANG=\"en_US.UTF-8\"\r\n```",
